# Real Estate Listings Search

A full-stack real estate search application demonstrating **role-aware listing search** with filters, pagination, and property detail views.

- **Frontend:** React  
- **Backend:** FastAPI (Python)  
- **Database:** PostgreSQL  
- **Containerization:** Docker  

---

## Features

- Search listings by:
  - Price range
  - Beds, baths
  - Property type
  - Keyword
  - Suburb
- View property detail
- Role-based behavior:
  - **Admins** see internal notes and status
  - **Normal users** see public fields only
- Pagination support (`limit` & `offset`)
- Fully containerized using Docker

---

## Prerequisites

- [Docker](https://www.docker.com/get-started)  
- [Docker Compose](https://docs.docker.com/compose/install/)  
- (Optional) Postman for API testing

---

## Commands to Run the App

### Build and start everything

```bash
docker-compose up --build
```
---

### Stopping 
```bash
docker-compose down
```

---

## Database Migration

```bash
docker-compose run migrate
```

---

### Sample API Request

Please refer to the attached `postman.json` collection for example API calls, including:

- **GET /listings** with filters (`min`, `beds`, etc.)  
- **GET /listings/{id}** for property details  
- Role-aware requests using the `X-User-Role` header (`admin` vs `user`)  

> Import the `postman.json` file into Postman to try out all endpoints quickly.